    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Menu\nSAS\nEUROCLASS",
      "BarService\nALERTES\nCocktails\nSherry\nCampari\nWINES\nChampagne Brut\nSelected red and white wines from\nsome of the world's finest vineyards\nGammel Dansk Bitters\nAalborg, Loiten and O.P. Andersson Aquavit\nBeefeater Gin\nBacardi Rum\nWHISKIES\nChivas Regal 12 year old Scotch\n1w. Marer DOwr00%\nCOGNAC \u0026 LIQUEURS\nRenault Carte Noire\nGrana Marnier\nPeter Heering\nDrambuie\nComtreau\nSCANDINAVIAN BEER\nVon-alcoholic wines\nare also available.\nMenu\nCOPENHAGEN-SEATTLE\nROSAD SEE SMON FUME.\nFILET DE LIMANDE A LA MEUNIERE\nFried Fillet of Dab\nPOMMES DE TERRE DUCHESSE\nDuchess Potatoes\nMACEDOINE DE LEGUMES\nMixed Vegetables\nOU/or\nSUPREME DE POULET POCHE,\nSAUCE AUX HERBES\nPoached Breast of Chicken with Herb Sauce\nRIZ ET CHOUX BROCOLIS\nRice and Broccoli\nPLATEAU DE FROMAGES\nCheese Served from the Cheese Board\nCREME BAVAROISE A LA DANOISE\nVanilla Bavarian Cream with Cherry Heering Jelly\nCAFE\nCoffee\nAVANT L'ATTERRISSAGE/Before landing\nHARENGS FRAIS SCANDINAVES\nScandinavian Herring\nTARTINE SUEDOISE\nSwedish Open-faced Sandwich\nCAFE ET CHOCOLATS\nCoffee and Chocolates"
    ],
